dcterms:creator: Xuemei Gu
dcterms:description: A dataset containing various optical setups used for training a deep learning model to predict quantum Fisher information.
dcterms:title: Training dataset for optical setups

dcterms:description: Datasets used for evaluating the performance of the deep learning model on tasks involving different sizes and numbers of photons.
dcterms:title: Datasets with different sizes and numbers of photons

dcterms:description: Datasets specifically designed for 4-photon and 8-photon tasks to assess the model's performance in quantum sensing.
dcterms:title: 4-photon and 8-photon tasks datasets

dcterms:description: A dataset containing 10,000 test samples in the latent space for evaluating the model's predictions.
dcterms:title: 10,000 test samples in the latent space

dcterms:description: A dataset containing 50,000 new samples specifically for the 8-photon quantum sensing task.
dcterms:title: 50,000 new samples for 8-photon quantum sensing task

dcterms:description: A dataset containing 30,000 training examples used for training the Graph Neural Network model.
dcterms:title: 30,000 training examples for GNN model

dcterms:description: A dataset containing 15,000 examples that include two optimal setups for quantum sensing tasks.
dcterms:title: 15,000 examples including two optimal setups

dcterms:description: A dataset containing 25,000 training examples that do not include optimal setups.
dcterms:title: 25,000 training examples without optimal setups

dcterms:description: A dataset containing 10,000 test examples with one optimal optical setup for evaluation purposes.
dcterms:title: 10,000 test examples with one optimal optical setup

dcterms:description: A dataset containing 100,000 training examples specifically for two-photon interactions.
dcterms:title: 100,000 training examples for two-photon interactions
